Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.06,0:00:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（一九六九年三月三日）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.12,0:00:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（美国海军为战机师 成立了一间精英学校）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.13,0:00:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（目的是教导机师 快将失传的空战技巧）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.13,0:00:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（以确保在此毕业的 一小撮机师）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.13,0:00:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（成为世上最一流的战机师）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.94,0:00:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（他们成功了）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.14,0:00:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（现在 海军称之为战斗学校）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.14,0:00:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（战机师则称之为 顶级机师部）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.27,0:01:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}壮志凌云{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.19,0:04:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（印度洋，现代）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.70,0:04:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 史葛，早 - 温斯，早{\r}\N-Morning, Scott  -Morning, Vince
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.40,0:04:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 威斯，早 - 长官，早{\r}\N-Morning, Wells  -Morning, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.47,0:04:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你好吗？{\r}\NOkey
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}骑鬼者，这儿是空袭部{\r}\NGhost Rider, this is Strike
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.78,0:04:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}发现不明战机，回程的军官{\r}\NWe have unknown aircraft Inbound, Mustang
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.98,0:04:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}循090方飞向敌机{\r}\NYour vector, 0-9-0 for bogey
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.36,0:04:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}上面的是谁？{\r}\NWho's up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.63,0:04:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}美洲狮、灰背隼 马华力和野鹅{\r}\NCougar and Merlin and Maverick and Goose
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}好极，是马华力和野鹅{\r}\NGreat Maverick and Goose
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.77,0:04:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}野鹅，快回答{\r}\NTalk to me, Goose
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.61,0:04:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}收到，我看到他了{\r}\NRoger, I got him.Contact, 20 left at 30 miles
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.61,0:04:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}在左面三十哩 以时速九百海海里飞近{\r}\NNine hundred knots closure
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.18,0:04:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}美洲狮，你听到吗？{\r}\NCougar, you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.08,0:04:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}收到{\r}\NRoger
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.55,0:05:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 灰背隼，看到他吗？ - 收到，雷达探测到了{\r}\N-Merlin, you got him?  -Roger, I've got radar contact
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我要亲眼确定他 美洲狮，你去引他上钓{\r}\NI'll get a visual ID.Cougar, you hook him
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.09,0:05:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}收到，我会将他煎皮拆骨{\r}\NRoger, and I'll clean him and fry him
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.13,0:05:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}军官，这是骑鬼者 我们在203方{\r}\NMustang, Mustang, this is Ghost Rider, 2-0-3,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他受制于我了 他向270方前进{\r}\NI've got him inbound, bogey heading 2-7-0,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.51,0:05:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}距离十哩，以九百海海里前进{\r}\NWe're at ten miles, 900 knots closure,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}骑鬼者，向上十度 向左三度、零{\r}\NGhost Rider, take Angels ten left, 3-0
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.55,0:05:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 我们今天应该有访客吗？ - 不{\r}\NAre we supposed to have visitors today? Negative, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.99,0:05:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}灰背隼，看看他是不是一个人{\r}\N-Merlin, see if he's a single
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.52,0:05:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}收到{\r}\N -Roger
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}野鹅，看到跟踪者吗？{\r}\NGoose, you see a trailer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}没有，灰背隼{\r}\NNegative, Merlin
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}似乎只有他一个{\r}\NLooks like he's a single
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.30,0:05:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}美洲狮，我要和他正面交锋{\r}\NCougar, I'm gonna go head-to-head with him
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.00,0:05:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}马华力，别乱来，我不同意{\r}\NTake it easy, Maverick I don't like this shit
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.44,0:05:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我飞高一些 确定是不是只有他一个{\r}\NI'm gonna break high and right,see if he's really alone
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.29,0:06:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}马华力，他以一千海海里接近{\r}\NWe've got 1000 knots closure, Mav
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.23,0:06:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他向着我们飞过来{\r}\NHe's coming right at us
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}老友，你在想什么？{\r}\NOkay, buddy, what's on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.33,0:06:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}天啊，他们有两个人{\r}\NHoly shit, there's two of them
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.07,0:06:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}是米格28 没人试过这么近看到{\r}\NMiG-28s No one's been this close before
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.30,0:06:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他们究竟在做什么？ 什么位置？{\r}\NWhat the hell are they doing here?What's the position?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}距离二百五十哩{\r}\NTwo hundred and fifty miles out, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.48,0:06:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}二百五十哩，叫他们马上离开{\r}\NTwo hundred and fifty miles? Get them out
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.11,0:06:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}美洲狮，你看到米格机一号 我去追二号{\r}\NCougar, you've got MiG one.I'm going after MiG two
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.32,0:06:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我在阳光下不见了他{\r}\NI lost him in the sun
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}该死，他在做什么？ 灰背隼，你制住他了吗？{\r}\NShit What's he doing? You got him, Merlin?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.36,0:06:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他在四处飞，他跟着我们飞{\r}\NHe's coming around.He's coming around on our tail
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.96,0:06:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}该死，被他制住了{\r}\NGoddamn it This bogey's all over me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:07:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 现在距离多远？ - 二百哩{\r}\N-What's their range now?  -Two hundred miles, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.11,0:07:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}短过一百五十哩的话 就出动五号戒备机{\r}\NIf they break 150 miles, launch the Alert Five aircraft
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.94,0:07:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}是，长官{\r}\NYes, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}空速三百，马华力，消灭他{\r}\NAir speed, 300 Go get him, Mav
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.85,0:07:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我准备锁定导弹{\r}\NI'm going for missile lock
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}看看能不能把他吓走{\r}\NLet's see if we can scare this guy out of here
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.49,0:07:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}快锁定，亲爱的{\r}\NCome on, lock up, baby.Lock up, baby Lock up
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.52,0:07:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}锁定吧，已经锁定了{\r}\NI got him locked Bingo
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.83,0:07:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}吓倒他了，马华力 他夹着尾巴逃走{\r}\NWe got him, Mav He's bugging out and going home
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}军官，我是马华力 米格机二号回去了{\r}\NMustang, this is Maverick MiG two is headed home
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.74,0:07:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}好吧，他们是什么位置？{\r}\NAll right What's their position?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.14,0:07:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}距离一百八十哩，方位是010{\r}\NA hundred and eighty miles at bearing 0-1-0, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.65,0:07:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他的导弹瞄准我们了 快点避开他{\r}\NCougar, he's got missile lock on us.Get away from this guy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.28,0:07:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这是怎么一回事？他追着我{\r}\NWhat the hell is this shit? He's engaging me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.19,0:07:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}该死，军官 这是骑鬼者117号{\r}\NGoddamn it, Mustang.This is Ghost Rider, 1-1-7
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我被敌机制住了 他用导弹锁定我了{\r}\NThis bogey's all over me He's got missile lock on me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.69,0:07:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我能得到开火的批准吗？{\r}\N Permission to fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.89,0:07:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}未受袭前不能开火{\r}\NDo not fire until fired upon
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.16,0:08:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}野鹅，他们就在我们下面{\r}\NGoose, there they are, right below us
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.63,0:08:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}米格机在最佳的开火位置 他在美洲狮后面{\r}\NThe MiG's in perfect firing position.He's right on Cougar's tail
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.54,0:08:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不可能，野鹅{\r}\NNo way, Goose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他早就应该开火了 他只是想激怒我们{\r}\NHe'd have fired by now He's just trying to piss us off
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.01,0:08:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}马华力，快来帮我脱身{\r}\NMaverick, get down here and get this asshole off me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.24,0:08:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}美洲狮，别紧张{\r}\NEasy, Cougar
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}带他回来，协助我进入战场{\r}\NBring it back, hard right Help me engage
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.65,0:08:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我来了{\r}\NI'm on my way
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.07,0:08:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我无法射击这个王八蛋{\r}\NI can't shoot this son of a bitch
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.67,0:08:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}看看我们能不能跟他玩玩{\r}\NLet's see if we can have a little fun with him
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.91,0:08:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你说的“玩玩”就是这样？{\r}\NIs this your idea of fun, Mav?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.45,0:08:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你好{\r}\NGreetings
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.55,0:08:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}小心战机{\r}\NWatch the birdie
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.69,0:09:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}天啊，笑死我了{\r}\NJeez, I crack myself up
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.57,0:09:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这种景象很精彩 我应该当摄影师{\r}\NThis is a great shot, Mav I should be a photographer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.00,0:09:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}美洲狮{\r}\NCougar
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.31,0:09:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你脱身了，米格机一号离开了{\r}\Nyour tail is clear MiG one's bugged out
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}美洲狮，我是马华力{\r}\NCougar, this is Maverick
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.42,0:09:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}今天玩得真开心呢，是吗？{\r}\NWe've had enough fun for one day, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.12,0:09:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}燃料不多了，我们回去吧{\r}\NI'm getting a little low on fuel, so we're heading home
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.20,0:09:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}在甲板上见{\r}\NWe'll see you on deck
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.91,0:09:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}飞洲狮，燃料不多，要走了{\r}\NCougar, we're running low on gas,we gotta get out of here
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.88,0:09:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}美洲狮{\r}\NCougar
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.78,0:10:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}快没燃料了，美洲狮，快回去{\r}\NWe're on vapor, Cougar Let's do it
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.22,0:10:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}美洲狮，快回去{\r}\NCougar Come on, Cougar
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.30,0:10:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}快飞回舰上，飞洲狮{\r}\NLet's take it back to the ship, man, Come on, Cougar,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.67,0:10:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}叫他尽快降落，他快没燃料了{\r}\NGet him on deck as soon as possible.He's gotta be low on fuel
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.21,0:10:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}美洲狮，我们要降落{\r}\NCougar, we gotta land this thing
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.84,0:10:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们快没燃料了，你明白吗？{\r}\NWe are way low on gas You understand me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.05,0:10:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你没事吧？{\r}\NYou all right, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.15,0:10:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}马华力，还有四分三哩 降落时作出通知{\r}\NMaverick, you're at three-quarters of a mile, call the ball,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.49,0:10:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}收到，马华力快要降落{\r}\NRoger Maverick has the ball
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.06,0:10:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}美洲狮，要降落了，快点回去{\r}\NCougar, it is time to land, Let's do it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.76,0:10:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}野鹅，美洲狮出了事{\r}\NGoose, Cougar's in trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.40,0:10:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}别乱来，我们快没燃料了 快点降落{\r}\NCome on, Mav, we're getting low on gas.Let's land this sucker
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.74,0:10:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}美洲狮{\r}\NCougar
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.91,0:11:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}该死，马华力{\r}\NGoddamn it, Maverick
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.28,0:11:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你在做什么？ 我们不够燃料这样做{\r}\NWhat are you doing, Mav?we've got no fuel for this
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.38,0:11:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们要去帮美洲狮{\r}\NWe're going after Cougar
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.35,0:11:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}叫他马上降落，这是命令{\r}\NYou tell him to land that plane That's an order
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.75,0:11:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}骑鬼者，你接到降落指示{\r}\NGhost Rider, you are instructed to land,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.79,0:11:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}马上降落{\r}\NLand immediately,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.06,0:11:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你们看到附近有航空母舰吗？{\r}\NAny of you boys seen an aircraft carrier around here?
