Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.93,0:12:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}美洲狮，太低了{\r}\NWe're too low, Cougar
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.94,0:12:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}加大动力{\r}\NIncrease power Some more power!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.88,0:12:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}请进{\r}\NCome in
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.69,0:12:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}长官{\r}\NSir
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.92,0:12:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}美洲狮，你应该在医护室的 你在想什么？{\r}\NCougar, you should be in sickbay.What's on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.69,0:12:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我的妻儿{\r}\NMy wife and kid, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.06,0:13:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他今天几乎变成孤儿 我从没见过他{\r}\NI almost orphaned him today, and I've never even seen him
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.40,0:13:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我不知道发生了什么事 但是我很害怕{\r}\NI don't know what happened up there, but I was so scared
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.04,0:13:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}别这样 我们以前也见过这种事{\r}\N-Come on, we've seen this before
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.57,0:13:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不，长官{\r}\N-No, sir
