Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.91,0:13:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我已经受够了，对不起，长官{\r}\NI've lost the edge I'm sorry, sir I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}美洲狮{\r}\NCougar
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.66,0:13:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}谢谢，马华力{\r}\NThanks, Maverick
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.57,0:13:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}马华力、野鹅，进来{\r}\NMaverick, Goose, come in here
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.43,0:13:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 发生了什么事？ - 我不知道{\r}\N-What the hell's going on?  -I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.62,0:13:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.41,0:13:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}马华力，你刚才做的事很勇敢{\r}\NMaverick, you just did an incredibly brave thing
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.55,0:13:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}可是你应该做的是降落{\r}\NWhat you should have done was land your plane
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.42,0:13:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}战机是纳税人的，不是你的{\r}\NYou don't own that plane, the taxpayers do
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.12,0:14:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你真是狂妄自大{\r}\NSon, your ego is writing checks your body can't cash
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.53,0:14:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你试过被开除 失去当小组队长的资格三次{\r}\NYou've been busted.You lost your qualifications as section leader three times
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我两次帮你恢复职位{\r}\NPut in hack twice by me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.73,0:14:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你却试过高速 飞过控制塔和上将之女{\r}\NWith a history of high-speed passes over five air-control towers and one admiral's daughter
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.47,0:14:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}班萍妮？{\r}\NPenny Benjamin?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.31,0:14:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 你这笨蛋能在这儿真是走运 - 谢谢{\r}\N-And you, asshole You're lucky to be here  -Thank you, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.51,0:14:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}别再说废话，马华力 你的家人不是空军中最好的{\r}\NLet's not bullshit, Maverick,your family name ain't the best in the Navy
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.28,0:14:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你应该比他做得更好 你究竟在想什么？{\r}\NYou need to be doing it better and cleaner than the other guy. Now, what is it with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.12,0:14:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我只想为国效力 当最好的海军战机师{\r}\NJust wanna serve my country,be the best fighter pilot in Navy, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.19,0:14:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}马华力，别骗我了{\r}\NDon't screw around with me, Maverick
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.96,0:14:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你全凭直觉当机师 而且很出色{\r}\NYou're a hell of an instinctive pilot Maybe too good
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.36,0:14:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我很想开除你 不过我有另一个麻烦{\r}\NI'd like to bust your butt, but I can't.I got another problem here
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.20,0:14:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我要从队中派人去米拉马{\r}\NI gotta send somebody from this squadron to Miramar
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.91,0:14:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我要做一些事 我难以置信的事{\r}\NI gotta do something here.I still can't believe it
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.38,0:14:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我要让你梦想成真 派你去面对一流的海军{\r}\NI gotta give you your dream shot.I'm gonna send you up against the best
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.31,0:14:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你们两个会进顶级机师部{\r}\NYou two characters are going to Top Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.78,0:15:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你们会和世上的顶级机师 交手五星期{\r}\NFor five weeks,you're gonna fly against the best fighter pilots in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.32,0:15:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你是第二，美洲狮是第一{\r}\NYou were number two, Cougar was number one
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.76,0:15:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}美洲狮放弃开战机{\r}\NCougar lost it, turned in his wings
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你们就成了第一{\r}\NYou guys are number one
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.70,0:15:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}记着一件事 你们闯过这么多祸{\r}\NBut you remember one thing: You screw up just this much,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}迟早会被调往运送狗屎的{\r}\Nyou'll be flying a cargo plane full of rubber dog shit out of Hong Kong
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}是，长官{\r}\NYes, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.51,0:15:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}没事了{\r}\NThat is all
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.51,0:15:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}改天把米格机的事告诉我{\r}\NYou can tell me about the MiG some other time
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.08,0:15:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}两位{\r}\NGentlemen
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.72,0:15:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}祝你们好运{\r}\N-Good luck, gentlemen  -Thank you, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}谢谢{\r}\NThank you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（美国空军基地 加州米拉马）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}海军在韩战的杀敌比率 是十二比一{\r}\NDuring Korea, the Navy kill ratio was 12-to-1
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,0:16:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们一架战机 就能击落敌人十二架{\r}\NWe shot down 12 of their jets for every one of ours
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.10,0:16:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}到了越战时比率降至三比一{\r}\NDuring Vietnam, that ratio fell to 3-to-1
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.64,0:16:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们的机师太依赖导弹了{\r}\NOur pilots become dependent upon missiles
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.84,0:16:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他们失去了一些空战技巧{\r}\NThey had lost some of their dogfighting skills
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.44,0:16:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}成立顶级机师部 是为了教导你们空战策略{\r}\NTop Gun was created to teach ACM: Air Combat Maneuvering
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.98,0:16:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}也就是空中格斗{\r}\NDogfighting
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.41,0:16:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}真令人兴奋{\r}\NThis gives me a hard-on
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.98,0:16:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}到了越战末期 比率回升至十二比一{\r}\NBy the end of Vietnam, that ratio was back up to 12-to-1
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}别跟我开玩笑{\r}\N-Don't tease me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.09,0:16:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}请下窗帘{\r}\N-Blinds, please
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.99,0:16:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我想藉着这次机会 介绍指挥官给大家认识{\r}\NI'd like to take this opportunity to introduce you to our commanding officer at Top Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.73,0:16:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他是第一位获得 顶级机师奖的人{\r}\NThe very first man to win the Top Gun trophy
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.16,0:16:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你不会在其他地方找到 比他更优秀的机师了{\r}\NYou will not find a finer fighter pilot anywhere in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.63,0:16:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}麦米克长官，外号毒蛇{\r}\NCommander Mike Metcalf Callsign: Viper
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.57,0:16:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}各位{\r}\NGentlemen
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你们是海军空战人员中 最好的百分之一{\r}\NYou are the top one percent of all naval aviators
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.11,0:17:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}是精英，精英中之精英{\r}\NThe elite The best of the best
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.18,0:17:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们会令你们更进一步{\r}\NWe'll make you better
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.05,0:17:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你们每天至少 要执行两项空中任务{\r}\NYou'll fly at least two combat missions a day,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.25,0:17:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}当中要上课 听取自己表现所得到的评价{\r}\Nattend classes in between and evaluations of your performance
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.02,0:17:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你们在每次的空中任务 都要面对新挑战{\r}\NOn each combat sequence, you're gonna meet a different challenge
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.76,0:17:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}每一次都会更加困难{\r}\NEvery encounter is gonna be much more difficult
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.13,0:17:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们会教你们 令F14尽展所长{\r}\NWe're gonna teach you to fly the F-14 right to the edge of the envelope,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.00,0:17:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你们会比以前开得更快{\r}\Nfaster than you've ever flown before
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.14,0:17:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}也会更加危险{\r}\Nand more dangerous
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.47,0:17:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}各位，我们不是在这儿立法{\r}\NNow, we don't make policy here, gentlemen
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.14,0:17:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}立法是由获选的官员 和平民做的{\r}\NElected officials, civilians do that
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.38,0:17:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们只是这些政策的工具{\r}\NWe are the instruments of that policy
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.48,0:17:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}虽然我们不是在打仗 但要假装是{\r}\NAnd although we're not at war,we must always act as though we are at war
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你在做什么？{\r}\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.95,0:17:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我只是在想谁是最一流的机师{\r}\N-The tip of the spear best be sharp  -I'm just wondering who's the best
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.36,0:17:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你们可能会想 谁是最一流的机师{\r}\NIn case some of you wonder who the best is,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:17:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他们的名字就在墙上的板子上{\r}\Nthey're up here on this plaque on the wall
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.46,0:18:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}最佳机师和他的通讯员的名字 都会记录在上面{\r}\NThe best driver and his RIO from each class has his name on it
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.87,0:18:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他们可以选择回来当教官{\r}\NAnd they have the option to come back here to be Top Gun instructors
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.21,0:18:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你认为你的名字会在上面？{\r}\NYou think your name's gonna be on that plaque?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}是，长官{\r}\NYes, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.01,0:18:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你真自大，周围有这么多人{\r}\NThat's pretty arrogant, considering the company you're in
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.62,0:18:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}是，长官{\r}\NYes, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.06,0:18:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我喜欢机师自大{\r}\NI like that in a pilot
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.83,0:18:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}记着，离开这儿后 我们都是同一队人{\r}\NJust remember, when it's over out there,we're all on the same team
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.20,0:18:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}各位，这儿是教大家战斗的{\r}\NGentlemen, this school is about combat
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.97,0:18:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}当第二是没意思的{\r}\NThere are no points for second place
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.81,0:18:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}解散{\r}\NDismissed
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}做得好{\r}\NNice going
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.01,0:18:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}后补者的徽章在女洗手间{\r}\NThe plaque for the alternates is down in the ladies' room
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.32,0:18:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}天啊，真是笑死我了{\r}\NOh, Jesus Oh, you kill me You really do
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.32,0:19:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不，“野鹅” 是两个O的{\r}\NNo, no, no There's two O's in "Goose", boys
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.87,0:19:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}真是一个不愁没目标的环境{\r}\NThis is what I call a target-rich environment
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.54,0:19:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你在两腿之间生活{\r}\NYou live your life between your legs, Mav
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.11,0:19:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}野鹅，连你也可以来这儿{\r}\NGoose, even you could get laid in a place like this
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.15,0:19:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}能找到说脏话的女孩 我就高兴了{\r}\NI'm telling you, I'd be happy to find a girl who'd talk dirty to me
