Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.70,0:35:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}两位，你们第一天过得真充实{\r}\NGentlemen You had a hell of a first day
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.70,0:35:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这次任务的假设地面是一万英尺{\r}\NThe hard deck for this hop was 10000 feet
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.07,0:35:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你们明知故犯{\r}\NYou knew it, you broke it
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.11,0:35:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}希军官不见了你们之后 你们跟着他低飞{\r}\NYou followed Commander Heatherly below after he lost sight of you and called no joy
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.68,0:35:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}为什么？{\r}\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.15,0:35:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}长官，我看到希军官{\r}\NSir I had Commander Heatherly in my sights.He saw me move in for the kill
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.26,0:35:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他看到我飞到开火的位置 就飞低过假设地面{\r}\NHe then proceeded below the hard deck
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.96,0:35:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们只有几秒低飞了{\r}\NWe weren't below 10000 for more than a few seconds
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.56,0:35:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我瞄准了他 见没有危险就开火{\r}\NI had the shot, there was no danger, so I took it
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.97,0:35:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你开了火，你破坏了重要守则{\r}\NYou took it And broke a major rule of engagement
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.97,0:36:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}飞越控制塔时又犯了另一条{\r}\NThen you broke another one with that circus-stunt flyby
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.28,0:36:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}麦上尉{\r}\NLieutenant Mitchell, Top Gun rules of engagement exist
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.65,0:36:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}守则是为了你 和队员的安全而设立的{\r}\Nfor your safety and for that of your team
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.75,0:36:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}守则不可随时更改，我也是{\r}\NThey are not flexible, nor am I
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.02,0:36:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不遵守的话就要被开除 清楚了吗？{\r}\NEither obey them or you're history.Is that clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.16,0:36:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}是，长官{\r}\NYes, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.14,0:36:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}解散{\r}\NDismissed
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.18,0:36:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我真的很享受那一下，谢谢你{\r}\NI really enjoyed that, Mav, thanks a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.68,0:36:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}天啊{\r}\NHoly shit
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.69,0:36:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我或者可以学习当货车司机{\r}\NMaybe I could learn how to be a truck driver
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.02,0:36:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你有货车驾驶学校的电话号码{\r}\NMav, you have the number of that truck-driving school we saw on TV?Truck Master, I think it is
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.99,0:36:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我可能会需要到{\r}\NI might need that
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.60,0:36:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}评估报告已经显示了他很飘忽{\r}\NHis fitness report says it all.He's a wild card
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.47,0:37:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他靠直觉开战机 完全无法预测{\r}\NFlies by the seat of his pants.Completely unpredictable
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.57,0:37:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 他吓倒你了？ - 是{\r}\N-He got you, didn't he?  -Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.11,0:37:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}马华力，我曾经和他爸爸共事{\r}\NMaverick I flew with his old man
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.85,0:37:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}告诉我 你想和他一起上战场吗？{\r}\NTell me one thing.If you had to go into battle, would you want him with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.42,0:37:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我不知道{\r}\NI don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.39,0:37:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我真的不知道{\r}\NI just don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.77,0:37:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}还没睡吗？{\r}\N-You still awake? 
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.74,0:37:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}是{\r}\N -Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.64,0:37:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你在想什么？{\r}\NWhat's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.71,0:37:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}睡不着{\r}\NCan't sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.85,0:37:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我知道可以进顶级机师部时 我只想拿机师奖{\r}\NYou know, when I first realized that we were going to Top Gun, all I could think about was getting that trophy
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.62,0:37:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我要坦白跟你说{\r}\NI gotta be straight with you, Mav
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.13,0:37:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我现在只希望我们能毕业{\r}\NRight now, I just hope we graduate
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.66,0:38:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我有家人 我不能浪费这个机会{\r}\NI got a family to think about.I can't afford to blow this
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.04,0:38:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}其实飞越控制塔不算什么{\r}\NYeah, I guess that flyby wasn't such a big hit
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.51,0:38:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我知道你很难受{\r}\NLook, man, I know it's tough for you
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.15,0:38:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他们因为你是麦杜克的儿子 而不让你进海军学院{\r}\NThey wouldn't let you in the academy because you're Duke Mitchell's kid
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.92,0:38:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你要承受这个污名{\r}\NYou have to live with that reputation
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.42,0:38:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们每次飞行时 你都像在面对鬼魂一样{\r}\NBut it's like every time we go up there,it's like you're flying against a ghost
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.46,0:38:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你令我紧张{\r}\NIt makes me nervous
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.20,0:38:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我只有你这个亲人{\r}\NYou're the only family I've got
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.90,0:38:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我不会令你失望的，我保证{\r}\NI'm not gonna let you down I promise you
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.02,0:38:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}出去吧{\r}\NGet out of here
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.60,0:39:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}在这情形下 倒转打转会很有效{\r}\NA rolling reversal would work well in that situation
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.07,0:39:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}如果我十字形倒转飞 就能马上转为发炮{\r}\NIf I reversed on a hard cross,I could immediately go to guns on them
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.24,0:39:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}在这种速度下，太快了{\r}\NYeah, but at that speed, it's too fast
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.75,0:39:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}而且太过急进{\r}\NIt's a little bit too aggressive
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.85,0:39:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}太过急进？{\r}\NToo aggressive
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.72,0:39:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我觉得应该这样做就这样做{\r}\NYeah, I guess when I see something,I go right after it
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.29,0:39:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你没告诉我你那晚去了哪儿{\r}\NYou didn't tell me who you were the other night
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.66,0:39:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你没有给我机会说{\r}\NYou didn't give me a chance, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.70,0:39:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你应有此报{\r}\NYou deserved it
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.93,0:39:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我知道 不过有人想你约我吃晚餐{\r}\NI know But you were tempted to ask me out for dinner
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.64,0:39:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不{\r}\N-No  -No?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.41,0:39:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 不？ - 我不和学员约会{\r}\NNo I don't date students
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.05,0:40:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我看得出这对你很危险{\r}\NI can see it's dangerous for you
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.66,0:40:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但是如果政府相信我 你也可以{\r}\NBut if the government trusts me, maybe you could
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.00,0:40:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这不只是花式飞行这么简单{\r}\NIt takes a lot more than just fancy flying
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.74,0:40:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（今晚五点半共进晚餐）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.85,0:40:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}一败涂地，马华力？{\r}\NCrash and burn, huh, Mav?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.76,0:40:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}滑行者{\r}\NSlider
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.93,0:40:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你很臭{\r}\Nyou stink
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.78,0:41:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}开始{\r}\NLet's go
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.94,0:41:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}冰佬，快打{\r}\NOkay, Ice, hit it
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.59,0:41:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good Come on
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.53,0:41:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, now
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.47,0:41:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Mav, 4-7 Let's get them.Those guys are animals
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.21,0:41:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.58,0:41:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good serve, good serve
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.21,0:42:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's game
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.95,0:42:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay Fake block, stay down.We'll just take them
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.52,0:42:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, where you guys going?You walking away?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.89,0:42:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won, we won
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.02,0:42:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}马华力，再打一局 就追成平手了{\r}\NMav Mav Come on, man.Just one more game That evens it up
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.16,0:42:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们很大机会会赢的 我们有实力{\r}\N-Come on, we can take them  -No
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.73,0:42:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我要去办一件事{\r}\N-No, we can, we got it  -I got some things I gotta take care of
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.33,0:42:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}办事？只是再打一局而已{\r}\NTake care of? Just one more game
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.80,0:42:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 为了我好吗？ - 对不起{\r}\N-Please? For me?  -I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.80,0:42:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你应该内疚，来吧{\r}\NYou're sorry Come on -Mother Goose, you pussy!  -For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.41,0:43:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}该死{\r}\NDamn it
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.79,0:43:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}上尉{\r}\NLieutenant?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.19,0:43:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不唱歌了吗？{\r}\NWhat, no singing?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.50,0:43:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 我... - 不用道歉{\r}\N-Look, I'm--I'm-- -No apologies
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.17,0:43:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你不介意的话 我想去快快洗一个澡{\r}\NIf you don't mind, I'm--I'm gonna just take a quick shower
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.58,0:43:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}让你好好吃完{\r}\Nwhile you're finishing up here
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.22,0:43:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}可是我介意，我很饿{\r}\NYeah, I do mind I'm hungry
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.06,0:44:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}后来我想起来了{\r}\NAnd then I thought about it
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.86,0:44:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我想{\r}\NI thought:
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.40,0:44:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}狐狸，他是个聪明人{\r}\NYou know, Charlie, he's a smart guy
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.60,0:44:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}为什么不干脆告诉他 请他来的目的？{\r}\NWhy don't you just tell him why you've got him here"
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.64,0:44:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}是什么？{\r}\NWell?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.27,0:44:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}米格机{\r}\NIt's the MiG
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.08,0:44:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}是米格机 只有你曾经面对过米格28{\r}\NThe MiG You're the only pilot who's been up against a MiG-28
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.19,0:44:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我正在努力工作 希望能够升职{\r}\NI'm trying for this big promotion at work, and if I get it,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.95,0:44:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}成功的话，我不会再留在这儿{\r}\NI'm not gonna be here much longer
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.76,0:44:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你似乎什么都想清楚了{\r}\NIt seems to me you've got it all figured out
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.03,0:44:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}是{\r}\NYeah
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.96,0:44:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}只是你忘记了酒{\r}\NExcept you did forget the wine
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.97,0:44:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}对不起{\r}\NSorry
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.87,0:44:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你常常如愿以偿？{\r}\NYou always get what you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.47,0:44:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不...可能是吧{\r}\NNo, not always Yeah, maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.88,0:44:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那就别这么在意那架米格机{\r}\NThen relax about the MiG
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.06,0:45:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这首音乐...{\r}\NThis music
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.63,0:45:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}是老朋友的？{\r}\NAn old friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.47,0:45:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我父母很喜欢这首音乐{\r}\NMy folks loved it
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.74,0:45:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我有很多年没听过了{\r}\NI haven't heard this in years
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.61,0:45:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}妈妈以前在房里 叫我把它不停重播{\r}\NMy mother used to call down from her room and have me play this over and over again
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.08,0:45:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我很厌倦听这首音乐{\r}\NI got so sick of it
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.69,0:45:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}她却没有{\r}\NBut not her, she
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.02,0:45:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}她会独坐在一旁 一听就听上几个小时{\r}\NJust sit up there alone, just listening, hours
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.39,0:45:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}她会跟着唱{\r}\NJust listening
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.33,0:45:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他死后不久她也死了{\r}\NShe died shortly after him
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.90,0:45:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你爸爸怎样死的？{\r}\NWhat happened to your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.11,0:46:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你既然有权知道机密资料{\r}\NI guess I kind of figured, with your security clearance,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.44,0:46:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}应该比我知道得更多{\r}\Nyou'd know more about him than I do
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.45,0:46:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我还没知道得这么深入{\r}\NWell, I didn't get that far
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.49,0:46:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这是一个谜{\r}\NWell, it's a big mystery
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.22,0:46:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他在1965年11月5日 开着F4失踪{\r}\NHe disappeared in an F-4, November 5th, 1965
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.50,0:46:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}听说是他犯错了，不可能{\r}\NThe stink of it was, he screwed up No way
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.07,0:46:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我爸爸是很优秀的机师{\r}\NMy old man was a great fighter pilot
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.08,0:46:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但谁知道呢？ 一切都被列作机密资料{\r}\NBut who the hell knows?It's all classified
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.68,0:46:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}一定有人知道的{\r}\NSomebody must know
