Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.47,1:13:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}天啊，他很喜欢和你并肩作战{\r}\NGod, he loved flying with you, Maverick
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.56,1:13:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}就算没遇上你，他也会当机师{\r}\NBut he'd have flown anyway without you
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.49,1:13:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}虽然他会讨厌这种事 但他还是会做{\r}\NHe'd have hated it, but he would've done it
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.15,1:14:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们发现这架F14的引擎 卷进了气流{\r}\NWe find that the F-14 flat spin was induced by the disruption of airflow into the starboard engine
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.49,1:14:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这种干扰令引擎 出现过多的偏航率{\r}\NThis disruption stalled the engine,which produced enough yaw rate
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.97,1:14:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}结果令机身不停打转 无法修正{\r}\Nto induce a spin which was unrecoverable
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.10,1:14:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这种问题 不是麦上尉可察觉到的{\r}\NThere was no way Lieutenant Mitchell could either see or avoid the jet wash which produced the engine stall
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.91,1:14:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}所以资询会发现{\r}\NTherefore, the board of inquiry finds that Lieutenant Pete Mitchell
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.95,1:14:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}麦彼得上尉 并没在7月29日的意外犯错{\r}\Nwas not at fault in the accident of 29 July
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.55,1:14:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这次的意外 不会记在麦上尉的纪录上{\r}\NLieutenant Mitchell's record will be cleared of this incident
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.35,1:14:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}麦上尉马上复职{\r}\NLieutenant Mitchell is restored to flight status without further delay
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.96,1:14:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}调查完毕{\r}\NThese proceedings are closed
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.03,1:14:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}尽快让他回复飞行{\r}\NGet him up flying, soon
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.23,1:15:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}小子，快点进战场{\r}\NCome on, kid, come on Get in there Engage
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.33,1:15:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}马华力，东北方有一架敌机{\r}\NAll right, you got a bogey at 2 o'clock low, Maverick
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.67,1:15:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你的位置很好 简直是轻而易举{\r}\NYou got the angle Piece of cake, pal
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.54,1:15:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}快开火，小子{\r}\NTake the shot, kid Take the shot
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.34,1:15:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}马华力，你随时都可以加入{\r}\NYou can engage any time, Maverick
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.32,1:15:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你要去哪儿？{\r}\NHey, where the hell are you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.79,1:15:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}情况不妙{\r}\NIt's not good It doesn't look good
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.36,1:15:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}情况不妙是什么意思？ 情况好到不得了{\r}\NWhat do you mean, it doesn't look good?It doesn't get to look any better than that
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.21,1:16:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你本来可以击中他的 我们可以击中他的{\r}\NHey, man, we could've had him.Hey, we could've had him, man!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.45,1:16:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我准备好时自然会发炮{\r}\NI will fire when I am goddamn good and ready!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.62,1:16:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你明白了吗？{\r}\NYou got that?!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.97,1:16:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他仍然未回复过来 他不愿战斗{\r}\NHe can't get back in the saddle Won't engage
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.91,1:16:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}只过了几天{\r}\NIt's only been a few days
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.38,1:16:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他可能不能回复过来{\r}\NYou know, he just might not make it back
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.05,1:16:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep sending him up
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.27,1:17:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}麦彼得{\r}\NMitchell
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.91,1:17:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我很难过野鹅死了{\r}\NI'm sorry about Goose
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.85,1:17:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}大家都喜欢他{\r}\NEverybody liked him
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.32,1:17:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我很难过{\r}\NI'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.44,1:17:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你好，我是人狼{\r}\NHi, it's Wolfman
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.31,1:17:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}马华力刚刚退学了{\r}\NYeah, Maverick just quit
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.81,1:18:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}对不起{\r}\NExcuse me
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.08,1:18:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我可以坐下吗？{\r}\NMay I?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.81,1:18:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}随便{\r}\NPlease
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.85,1:18:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}和他要的一样{\r}\NI'll have what he's having
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.93,1:18:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}是毒药吧{\r}\NHemlock, is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.79,1:18:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}是冰水{\r}\NIce water
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.17,1:18:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你不和我道别吗？{\r}\NYou weren't gonna say goodbye?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.41,1:18:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}听说你得到华盛顿的工作了{\r}\NI heard you got that job in Washington
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.41,1:18:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}恭喜{\r}\N Congratulations
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.28,1:18:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}谢谢{\r}\NThanks
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.68,1:18:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但是我不会不辞而别{\r}\NBut I wasn't gonna leave without saying goodbye
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.42,1:19:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}看到你真好{\r}\NIt's good to see you
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.22,1:19:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}谢谢{\r}\NThanks
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.59,1:19:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你要去哪儿？{\r}\NWhere you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.40,1:19:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你连机票也没有吧{\r}\NYou don't even have a ticket, do you?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.03,1:19:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我看过所有证据 这不是你的责任{\r}\NListen, I've seen all the evidence,and it's not your responsibility
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.01,1:19:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不是你的错 你是海军里的精英{\r}\NIt's not your fault You're one of the best pilots in the Navy
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.11,1:19:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你在高空战斗是很危险{\r}\NWhat you do up there, it's dangerous
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.68,1:19:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但是你得继续下去{\r}\NBut you've got to go on
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.02,1:19:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你不明白{\r}\NYou don't understand
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.89,1:19:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我刚认识你时 你的生活很充实{\r}\NWhen I first met you, you were larger than life
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.20,1:19:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}看看你{\r}\NLook at you
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.57,1:19:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你不过步伐急速的生活 你不会快乐{\r}\NYou're not gonna be happy unless you're going Mach 2 with your hair on fire,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.94,1:19:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你知道的{\r}\N-you know that  -No, it's over
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.87,1:19:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不，完了 做精英中的精英{\r}\N-It's just over  -To be the best of the best
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.68,1:20:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}就是犯错后仍然继续努力{\r}\Nmeans you make mistakes and then you go on.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.75,1:20:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这对大家来说都一样{\r}\NIt's just like the rest of us
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.25,1:20:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你以为我不知道吗？{\r}\NYou don't think I know that?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.42,1:20:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我是来帮你的{\r}\NI'm here to help
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.02,1:20:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}谢谢你{\r}\NLook, thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.86,1:20:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我想别人帮我的话 自然会开口{\r}\NBut if I wanted help, really,I would have asked for it
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.10,1:20:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}原来我来迟了{\r}\NSo I'm too late
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.41,1:20:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你已经离开了{\r}\NYou've already left
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.54,1:20:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你什么都没学到{\r}\NYou didn't learn a damn thing, did you?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.81,1:20:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你只学会退缩{\r}\NExcept to quit
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.02,1:20:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你真的很擅长做这种事呢{\r}\NYou've got that maneuver down real well
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.76,1:20:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}再见了，麦彼得{\r}\NSo long, Pete Mitchell
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.03,1:21:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你好，马华力，请进{\r}\NWell, hi, Maverick, come on in
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.49,1:21:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 你好吗？ - 我很好{\r}\N-How are you doing?  -Good
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.80,1:21:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 真的，你真的没事？ - 我很好{\r}\N-Really? You sure you're feeling okay?  -Oh, I feel great
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.50,1:21:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 珍美，你要喝点什么吗？ - 不必了{\r}\NJamie, come on.Can I get you a drink or anything else like that?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.26,1:21:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}请随便坐，米克马上就下来了{\r}\N-No, thank you  -Okay, well, why don't you just make yourself comfortable Mike will be right down
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.97,1:21:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}谢谢{\r}\NGreat, thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.39,1:21:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你爸爸和我在奥利士卡尼号的 VF51小队并肩作战{\r}\NI flew with your old man VF-51, the Oriskany
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.77,1:22:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你真的很像他{\r}\NYou're a lot like he was Only better and worse
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.04,1:22:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他是一个天生的英雄主义者{\r}\NHe was a natural heroic son of a bitch, that one
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.68,1:22:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他真的没做错{\r}\NSo he did do it right
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.99,1:22:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}是的，他没做错{\r}\NYeah, he did it right
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.17,1:22:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}所以你这样开战机？ 你想证明什么？{\r}\NIs that why you fly the way you do?Trying to prove something?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.51,1:22:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你爸爸的确没做错{\r}\NYeah, your old man did it right
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.58,1:22:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我要告诉你的事是机密事件 可能会令我丢掉工作{\r}\NWhat I'm about to tell you is classified.It could end my career
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.52,1:22:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们置身于一场 我梦寐以求的战斗之中{\r}\NWe were in the worst dogfight I ever dreamed of
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.89,1:22:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}敌机像萤火虫般布满天空{\r}\NBogies like fireflies all over the sky
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.76,1:23:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他的F4战机被击中，他受了伤{\r}\NHis F-4 was hit, he was wounded,but he could've made it back
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.36,1:23:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他本来可以回基地 但是他留在战场{\r}\NHe stayed in it, saved three planes 
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.70,1:23:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}在坠毁之前救了三架战机{\r}\Nbefore he bought it
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.07,1:23:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我怎么会从没听说过？{\r}\NHow come I never heard that before?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.60,1:23:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}州政府不会告诉家属{\r}\NThat's not something the State Department tells dependents
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.04,1:23:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}因为地图出错而发生战事{\r}\Nwhen the battle occurred over the wrong line on some map
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.58,1:23:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 你当时在场？ - 是{\r}\N-So you were there?  -I was there
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.92,1:23:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你在想什么？{\r}\NWhat's on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.99,1:23:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我的选择{\r}\NMy options, sir
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.12,1:23:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}很简单{\r}\NSimple
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.42,1:23:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你已经拿到足够分数 出席明天的毕业礼{\r}\NFirst, you've acquired enough points to show up tomorrow and graduate with your Top Gun class
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.23,1:23:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}否则就退学{\r}\NOr you can quit
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.37,1:23:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这不是丢脸的事 那样打转我也会被吓倒{\r}\NThere'd be no disgrace That spin was hell.It would've shook me up
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.37,1:23:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你认为我应该退学？{\r}\NSo you think I should quit?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.31,1:23:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我没说过{\r}\NI didn't say that
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.68,1:23:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你觉得是你害了野鹅 而且有信心危机{\r}\NThe simple fact is, you feel responsible for Goose,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.65,1:23:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我不会坐在这儿跟你说好话{\r}\NNow, I'm not gonna sit here and blow sunshine up your ass, lieutenant
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.09,1:24:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}一个好机师必须评估发生的事{\r}\NA good pilot is compelled to always evaluate what's happened
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.52,1:24:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这样才能学以致用{\r}\NSo he can apply what he's learned
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.19,1:24:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}到了高空我们就要全力以赴 这是我们的职责{\r}\NUp there, we gotta push it That's our job
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.44,1:24:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}上尉，这全看你的选择{\r}\NIt's your option, lieutenant, all yours
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.18,1:24:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}对不起，在周日打扰你{\r}\NSorry to bother you on a Sunday, sir,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.75,1:24:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}谢谢你抽空见我{\r}\Nbut thank you very much for your time
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.12,1:24:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不要紧，祝你好运{\r}\NNo problem Good luck
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.69,1:24:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}（房子出租）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.91,1:25:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}各位{\r}\N-Gentlemen  
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.34,1:25:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}马华力在哪儿？{\r}\N-Where's Maverick?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.71,1:25:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我不知道他在哪儿{\r}\NI don't know where he is
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.68,1:25:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你知道他有什么打算吗？{\r}\NYou know what he's planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.55,1:25:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他一定是很难过{\r}\NGotta be hard on the guy, though
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.45,1:26:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}恭喜{\r}\NCongratulations
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.29,1:26:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}谢谢{\r}\NThank you
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.89,1:26:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 恭喜 - 谢谢{\r}\N-Congratulations  -Thanks, Mav
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.29,1:26:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}长官{\r}\NSir
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.43,1:26:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}各位{\r}\NGentlemen
